narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If you are doing the senior essay in linguistics, you ought to take this course, of course. Seniors of generations past have walked this road. You will survive. Tip: work a little bit each week, and support your fellow seniors... Raffaella has been a great instructor for this course - encouraging and accommodating, and she gives helpful feedback. A lot of help actually came from classmates - your feedback to each other is useful, even if you're all doing different topics.
